DOES IT LOOKS ALL RIGHT?

00:06:05.965 --> 00:06:07.034
&gt;&gt; Kittan: LOOKS LIKE YOKO’S

00:06:07.034 --> 00:06:08.671
RIGHT.

00:06:08.671 --> 00:06:09.506
IT’S FAR BETTER TO CONCEAL

00:06:09.506 --> 00:06:11.008
THAN TO REVEAL.

