[boys laughing]

00:06:15.417 --> 00:06:19.458
&gt;&gt; Yoko: [stammering]

00:06:19.458 --> 00:06:20.561
&gt;&gt; Ron: YOU JEALOUS?

00:06:20.561 --> 00:06:21.395
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YEAH , RIGHT!

00:06:21.395 --> 00:06:22.431
