&gt;&gt; Yoko: [grunting]

00:07:14.034 --> 00:07:16.506
AAH!

00:07:18.409 --> 00:07:19.746
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHY, YOU STUPID

00:07:19.746 --> 00:07:20.815
LITTLE... COME BACK HERE!

00:07:20.815 --> 00:07:22.752
YOU...OHH!

00:07:22.752 --> 00:07:24.522
&gt;&gt; Nia: HAAH!

00:07:31.837 --> 00:07:32.739
MY GOODNESS.

00:07:32.739 --> 00:07:33.774
IT LOOKS LIKE I DID IT!

00:07:33.774 --> 00:07:35.978
&gt;&gt; all: NIA, YOU ARE SO AWESOME!

00:07:35.978 --> 00:07:38.784
&gt;&gt; Yoko: [growls]

00:07:40.821 --> 00:07:42.592
&gt;&gt; Ron: ALL RIGHT, EVERYBODY,

00:07:42.592 --> 00:07:43.794
