00:07:43.794 --> 00:07:45.130
I WILL NOW EXPLAIN TO YOU

00:07:45.130 --> 00:07:46.867
HOW MY AQUATIC EQUIPMENT WORKS.

00:07:46.867 --> 00:07:47.902
NOW LISTEN UP CLOSELY.

00:07:47.902 --> 00:07:50.073
FIRST OF ALL...

00:07:53.847 --> 00:07:57.120
&gt;&gt; Yoko: [grunting]

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:59.124
[gurgling]

00:07:59.124 --> 00:08:03.166
[chattering]

00:08:03.166 --> 00:08:04.201
&gt;&gt; Ron: SO WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:08:04.201 --> 00:08:05.170
&gt;&gt; Nia: [giggling]

00:08:05.170 --> 00:08:06.205
&gt;&gt; Ron: SHE’S COMPLETELY

00:08:06.205 --> 00:08:07.174
BLENDED IN.

00:08:07.174 --> 00:08:09.779
AND SHE’S A VERY SWEET GIRL.

00:08:09.779 --> 00:08:10.614
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YES, I KNOW ALL THAT,

00:08:10.614 --> 00:08:12.084
ALL RIGHT?

00:08:12.084 --> 00:08:13.252
&gt;&gt; Ron: YOU MAD THAT SHE’S

00:08:13.252 --> 00:08:14.989
STOLEN THE BOYS AWAY?

00:08:14.989 --> 00:08:16.192
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OF COURSE NOT.

00:08:16.192 --> 00:08:18.897
&gt;&gt; Ron: MM‐HMM.

00:08:18.897 --> 00:08:20.233
[chuckles]

00:08:20.233 --> 00:08:21.570
&gt;&gt; Kittan: AFTER YOU SWIM...

00:08:21.570 --> 00:08:23.206
YOU GOTTA HAVE A BARBECUE!

00:08:23.206 --> 00:08:25.243
&gt;&gt; Nia: HERE!

00:08:25.243 --> 00:08:27.481
&gt;&gt; Yoko: [gasps]

00:08:27.481 --> 00:08:29.519
&gt;&gt; Nia: HERE. GO ON, MISS YOKO.

00:08:29.519 --> 00:08:31.188
EAT UP!

00:08:31.188 --> 00:08:36.867
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH, WELL, OKAY.

00:08:36.867 --> 00:08:38.002
[gasps]

00:08:38.002 --> 00:08:40.240
[group groans]

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:41.108
&gt;&gt; Artenborough: YOKO WENT AND

00:08:41.108 --> 00:08:42.177
DROPPED HER CRAB!

00:08:42.177 --> 00:08:43.079
&gt;&gt; Kidd: NIA SLAVED AWAY TO

00:08:43.079 --> 00:08:44.148
MAKE THAT, YOU KNOW!

00:08:44.148 --> 00:08:48.524
&gt;&gt; all: AAH!

00:08:48.524 --> 00:08:49.993
[laughter]

00:08:49.993 --> 00:08:52.230
GOTCHA! JUST KIDDING!

00:08:52.230 --> 00:08:53.534
HUH?

00:08:53.534 --> 00:08:54.669
&gt;&gt; Nia: IT’S OKAY.

00:08:54.669 --> 00:08:56.272
I’LL MAKE YOU ANOTHER ONE.

00:08:56.272 --> 00:08:57.207
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’M SORRY,

00:08:57.207 --> 00:08:58.076
BUT DON’T BOTHER.

00:08:58.076 --> 00:08:59.713
I DON’T WANT ANY, OKAY?!

00:08:59.713 --> 00:09:01.550
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHY NOT, MISS YOKO?

00:09:01.550 --> 00:09:02.217
&gt;&gt; Kidd: WHAT THE HELL’S HER

00:09:02.217 --> 00:09:03.252
PROBLEM?

00:09:03.252 --> 00:09:04.254
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: LOOKS LIKE SOMEBODY

00:09:04.254 --> 00:09:05.524
CAN’T TAKE A JOKE!

00:09:05.524 --> 00:09:06.058
&gt;&gt; Jorgun: YEAH, IT JOKE.

