00:18:32.457 --> 00:18:33.627
NOW LISTEN UP.

00:18:33.627 --> 00:18:37.868
ON MY SIGNAL, BLOW IT TO PIECES.

00:18:37.868 --> 00:18:43.245
OR ELSE!

00:18:43.245 --> 00:18:45.249
&gt;&gt; all: YOKO!

00:18:45.249 --> 00:18:46.485
[gun locks and loads]

00:18:46.485 --> 00:18:49.190
[all gasp]

00:18:49.190 --> 00:18:50.326
&gt;&gt; Adiane: AND WHAT HAVE WE

00:18:50.326 --> 00:18:50.861
HERE?

00:18:50.861 --> 00:18:52.497
THAT TOY OF YOURS WON’T WORK ON

00:18:52.497 --> 00:18:54.234
MY SAYRUNE.

00:18:54.234 --> 00:18:55.469
OR ARE YOU GOING TO KILL THE

00:18:55.469 --> 00:18:56.773
PRINCESS AND REMOVE HER AS

00:18:56.773 --> 00:18:58.142
A BARGAINING CHIP?

00:18:58.142 --> 00:18:59.377
[Artenborough gasps]

00:18:59.377 --> 00:19:00.547
&gt;&gt; Tetsukan: YOKO!

00:19:00.547 --> 00:19:01.716
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: HEY, YOKO, WAIT UP.

00:19:01.716 --> 00:19:02.483
DON’T BE HASTY!

00:19:02.483 --> 00:19:03.687
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOKO, DON’T DO IT!

00:19:03.687 --> 00:19:06.258
&gt;&gt; Yoko: BE QUIET. SHUT UP.

00:19:13.172 --> 00:19:14.508
[all screaming]

00:19:14.508 --> 00:19:15.744
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOKO!

00:19:15.744 --> 00:19:17.548
&gt;&gt; Adiane: VERY INTERESTING...

00:19:17.548 --> 00:19:18.850
AND WHAT WILL YOU BE SHOOTING

00:19:18.850 --> 00:19:19.719
NEXT?

00:19:19.719 --> 00:19:21.355
PERHAPS AN ARM?

00:19:21.355 --> 00:19:22.390
MAYBE A LEG?

00:19:22.390 --> 00:19:23.325
IF YOU MAKE HER SUFFER TOO

00:19:23.325 --> 00:19:24.361
BADLY, I MIGHT START TO FEEL

00:19:24.361 --> 00:19:26.431
SORRY FOR THE GIRL!

00:19:36.284 --> 00:19:38.790
WHAT?

00:19:38.790 --> 00:19:41.729
MY SHOULDER!

00:19:50.680 --> 00:19:52.283
&gt;&gt; Nia: GRAMPS, IT’S YOU!

00:19:52.283 --> 00:19:53.385
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

00:19:53.385 --> 00:19:54.922
&gt;&gt; Old Coco: HEE.

00:19:54.922 --> 00:19:56.391
&gt;&gt; Adiane: CAREFUL!

00:19:56.391 --> 00:19:57.694
FIRE AT THAT ANGLE, AND YOU’LL

00:19:57.694 --> 00:20:00.199
MANAGE TO KILL BOTH OF US.

00:20:00.199 --> 00:20:00.967
YOU HUMANS AREN’T REALLY THAT

00:20:00.967 --> 00:20:02.270
STUPID, ARE YOU?

00:20:02.270 --> 00:20:04.274
&gt;&gt; Yoko: ACTUALLY...

00:20:04.274 --> 00:20:05.176
I’M AFRAID WE ARE.

00:20:05.176 --> 00:20:05.711
&gt;&gt; Artenborough: COME ON!

00:20:05.711 --> 00:20:06.512
TO HELL WITH IT!

00:20:06.512 --> 00:20:07.246
FIRE!

00:20:07.246 --> 00:20:08.248
[dramatic music]

00:20:08.248 --> 00:20:10.554
♪ ♪

00:20:10.554 --> 00:20:13.660
[Adiane gasps]

00:20:13.660 --> 00:20:17.701
&gt;&gt; Viral: GENERAL ADIANE!

00:20:17.701 --> 00:20:19.739
&gt;&gt; Simon: NO, YOU DON’T!

00:20:31.963 --> 00:20:35.269
&gt;&gt; Adiane: THYMILPH, I’M...

00:20:35.269 --> 00:20:37.473
I’M SORRY.

00:20:52.236 --> 00:20:54.508
[all cheering]

00:20:54.508 --> 00:20:55.510
&gt;&gt; Artenborough: LET’S RIDE

00:20:55.510 --> 00:20:58.950
THIS WAVE STRAIGHT TO SHORE!

00:21:05.864 --> 00:21:09.705
&gt;&gt; Lordgenome: HM?

00:21:09.705 --> 00:21:11.609
SHE’S DEAD?

00:21:11.609 --> 00:21:15.316
[both grumbling]

00:21:15.316 --> 00:21:16.586
[Viral exhales loudly]

00:21:16.586 --> 00:21:18.556
&gt;&gt; Viral: DAMN YOU!

00:21:18.556 --> 00:21:21.394
DAMN YOU, GURREN LAGANN!

00:21:21.394 --> 00:21:24.602
DAMN!

00:21:29.912 --> 00:21:31.549
&gt;&gt; Nia: MISS YOKO?

00:21:31.549 --> 00:21:32.985
WILL YOU DO ME A FAVOR?

00:21:32.985 --> 00:21:37.393
&gt;&gt; Yoko: HUH? SURE.

00:21:37.393 --> 00:21:38.362
&gt;&gt; Nia: I WOULD LIKE YOU...

00:21:38.362 --> 00:21:41.769
TO TIDY UP MY HAIR A BIT.

00:21:41.769 --> 00:21:44.708
[scissors snipping]

00:21:44.708 --> 00:21:46.579
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OOPS.

00:21:46.579 --> 00:21:48.315
THIS STUFF ISN’T EXACTLY MY

00:21:48.315 --> 00:21:49.518
STRONG SUIT.

00:21:49.518 --> 00:21:50.386
DON’T COME COMPLAINING TO ME

00:21:50.386 --> 00:21:51.956
AFTERWARDS.

00:21:51.956 --> 00:21:53.927
&gt;&gt; Nia: IT’LL BE FINE.

00:21:53.927 --> 00:21:54.929
&gt;&gt; Yoko: ANOTHER THING YOU

00:21:54.929 --> 00:21:55.697
JUST KNOW?

00:21:55.697 --> 00:21:56.899
&gt;&gt; Nia: YES!

00:21:56.899 --> 00:21:59.839
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OHH.

00:22:04.013 --> 00:22:05.349
WHY DID YOU CLOSE YOUR EYES

00:22:05.349 --> 00:22:06.919
BACK THERE?

00:22:06.919 --> 00:22:08.523
&gt;&gt; Nia: YOU ARE A MASTER

00:22:08.523 --> 00:22:09.725
WITH A RIFLE, MISS YOKO.

00:22:09.725 --> 00:22:11.394
I CLOSED MY EYES BECAUSE I HAD

00:22:11.394 --> 00:22:12.463
FAITH IN YOU.

00:22:12.463 --> 00:22:17.508
[Yoko gasps]

00:22:17.508 --> 00:22:19.778
&gt;&gt; Yoko: BOY...WHAT A MORON.

00:22:19.778 --> 00:22:20.580
&gt;&gt; Nia: HUH?

00:22:20.580 --> 00:22:21.448
&gt;&gt; Yoko: NO, NO!

00:22:21.448 --> 00:22:24.053
I WAS TALKING TO MYSELF.

00:22:24.053 --> 00:22:26.626
OKAY! ALL DONE!

00:22:26.626 --> 00:22:27.761
&gt;&gt; Nia: AH! THERE’S SOMETHING

00:22:27.761 --> 00:22:29.565
REFRESHING ABOUT IT.

00:22:29.565 --> 00:22:30.934
&gt;&gt; Yoko: REALLY?

00:22:30.934 --> 00:22:31.836
YOU THINK SO?

00:22:31.836 --> 00:22:33.506
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:22:33.506 --> 00:22:35.610
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WELL...IT’S NICE.

00:22:35.610 --> 00:22:39.518
&gt;&gt; Nia: YOU REALLY MEAN IT?

00:22:39.518 --> 00:22:43.125
[Yoko giggles]

00:22:46.999 --> 00:22:48.001
[rock music]

00:22:48.001 --> 00:22:54.447
♪ ♪

00:22:54.447 --> 00:22:55.449
[man singing in Japanese]

00:22:55.449 --> 00:23:03.533
♪ ♪

00:24:18.215 --> 00:24:19.217
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT WILL IT TAKE TO

00:24:19.217 --> 00:24:20.654
GET A SMILE OUT OF THE BOY WHO

00:24:20.654 --> 00:24:22.557
IS LOOKING UP INTO THE SKY?

00:24:22.557 --> 00:24:24.862
I WILL COOK DINNER AND WAIT FOR

00:24:24.862 --> 00:24:25.764
FOR HIM.

00:24:25.764 --> 00:24:28.503
NEXT TIME ON <i>GURREN LAGANN:</i>

00:24:28.503 --> 00:24:32.009
"EAT UP, EVERYONE."

